<L>__{interior university reading room several hours later}
<A>__{things have quieted down. the drama teacher has cornered frances and is gesticulating drunkenly, waving a copy of "voice of action." frances is also tipsy, but pays close attention to her mentor.}
<C>__{drama teacher}
<D>__{this is the answer: a subscription drive to "voice of action!" first prize is a trip to moscow! you could visit the art theatre, maybe even meet stanislavski!}
